      <div class="about" id="about">
        <h3>About Us</h3>
        <div class="para">
          <p>
            2Xcell is an A.I driven self-paced learning and assessment platform
            that helps a student become a ‘Super Learner’ using Hybrid and
            Blended Learning Model. It is designed keeping in mind the Future of
            Education and driving learning through data output and AI. Over the
            time it understands the teaching and assessment styles and starts
            taking over feedback.
          </p>
          <div class="thumbnail">
            <img src="/public/web/assets/images/about-us/Para-1.png" alt="para-1" />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="para">
          <div class="thumbnail">
            <img src="/public/web/assets/images/about-us/Para-2.png" alt="para-2" />
          </div>
          <p>
            In 2xcell, has advanced personalized learning algorithms and impact
            measurement tools designed to enhance educational outcomes. By
            continuously refining these tools based on cutting-edge research,
            technological advancements, and real-world data gathered from
            thousands of schools we have worked with.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="para">
          <p>
            Students get “Exclusive Personalized Learning under the guidance of
            their teacher and mentors, which strengthens the learning base of
            students. The interactive, immersive and customized digital
            resources in the form 3D-2D animated modules, self-learning
            activities, simulations, games, stories help them to upgrade their
            skills at a much faster pace.
          </p>
          <div class="slider">
            <div class="carousel">
              <div class="slides">
                <div class="slide">
