                    alt="Image 4"
                  />
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p>
            Inquiry-Based Learning (IBL) helps a student assess himself and
            measure the learning outcome /Learning index or Lx at subtopic level
            and provides remarkable insights to help teachers/mentor plan the
            right pedagogy for the student and design a personalized ‘Goal
            Oriented’ learning plan. Seamless integration of concepts across
            grades under the “Multi-Grade Program” helps students strengthen the
            base for the upcoming Grades and explore beyond the curriculum.
          </p>
